item.title: Looking for partners to a blank PI project
item.dc:creator: @Ez_Outlawz Ez Outlawz
item.description:
@Ez_Outlawz wrote:

[quote=“XxAndyxX, post:9, topic:437767”][quote author=Ez Outlawz link=topic=540468.msg3958805#msg3958805 date=1333057864]
Everyone knows how a Blank Pi looks like. No need of pictures of that lmao
[/quote]

I now have no interest in joining with you,

the pictures are only the beginning of your failure. You should’ve posted ideas of what you wanted accomplish as a team working with (PI), the images should have been of the similar nature but not limited to just what you had in mind.

Showing these things show that you are capable and willing to put time and effort into something and not just “Everyone knows how a Blank Pi looks like. No need of pictures of that lmao” Your lacking all evidence of any dedication whatsoever and by now have successfully filtered out anyone but morons.

The truly sad thing is you will end up accepting these said ‘morons’ spend less then 10 days on an already over cluster-fucked Project Insanity. Then one of your “Dream-Team” members will inevitably release this before completion without giving any credit to anyone but his\herself. Then this community will not only be forced to waste valuable time flaming you for releasing something completely useless and unoriginal just like this thread and yourself.

Theirs your next week or so of your life in a shell… Goodluck!

If i could I would Rep-- you[/quote]
OK BOSS. LOL
